Package com.itsradiix.discordwebhook.models.embeds

Class Embed

java.lang.Object
com.itsradiix.discordwebhook.models.embeds.Embed
public class Embed extends Object
Represents an embedded message that can be sent via a Discord webhook. Embedded messages allow for richly formatted content to be displayed within the message.

Make sure to read the wiki page on our GitHub to understand how to use this effectively: Discord-Webhooks Wiki

2024-05-19

    • hexToDecimal

      public static int hexToDecimal(String hex)
      This static method will translate Hex color codes to Decimal color codes as that's Discords standard. You can use various tools to get a Hex color, like: https://htmlcolorcodes.com/
      Parameters:
      hex - Set the border color of your Embedded Message. This must be a Hex color code.
      Returns:
      Decimal color used by discord
